  "text": "# CURRENT ACCOUNT  \n**Q: What is the Current Account?**\nA: Our checking account for everyday spending, with no monthly fees, standing orders, and optional overdraft facility.  \n**Q: What are the fees?**\nA: No monthly fee. Overdraft interest (if used) at 15% AER for arranged overdraft.  \n**Q: Can I set up standing orders?**\nA: Yes. Set up recurring payments to anyone, anytime.  \n**Q: Can I use Direct Debits?**\nA: Yes. Authorize billers to take payments automatically, with full protection under Direct Debit Guarantee.  \n**Q: Is there an overdraft?**\nA: Optional. You can arrange an overdraft limit of £500–£5,000 if eligible.  \n---",
